<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="chr.wilck;;378" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">WChr378</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><ab part="N">
    <lb n="1"/><app type="BL"><lem resp="2.2.92"><seg cert="low" part="N"><supplied cert="low" reason="lost">Ν</supplied>ερβαῖος</seg></lem><rdg><seg cert="low" part="N"><supplied cert="low" reason="lost">Σ</supplied>ερβαῖος</seg></rdg></app> Ἀφρικανὸς στρατηγοῖς ἐπι-

    <lb n="2"/>στρατηγίας ἑπτὰ νομῶν καὶ Ἀρσινοίτου 

    <lb n="3"/>χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="4"/>ἀπ᾽ αὐτῶν τῶν <choice><corr><supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">λ</supplied>όγων</corr><sic>ογων</sic></choice> ἐφάνη ὡς 

    <lb n="5"/>πολλοὶ βουλόμενοι τὰς ταμιακὰς οὐσί-

    <lb n="6"/>ας <choice><corr>κατεσθίειν</corr><sic>κατεστειειν</sic></choice> ὀνόματα ἑαυτοῖς ἐξευ-

    <lb n="7"/>ρόντες, οἱ μὲν χειριστῶν οἱ δὲ γραμ-

    <lb n="8"/>ματέων οἱ δὲ φροντιστῶν, ὄφελος 

    <lb n="9"/>μὲν οὐδὲν περιποιοῦσιν τῷ ταμείῳ 

    <lb n="10"/>τὰ δὲ περιγεινόμενα <choice><corr>κατεσθίουσιν</corr><sic>κατεστειουσιν</sic></choice>· 

    <lb n="11"/>δι᾽ ὅπερ ἐδέησεν ἐπισταλῆναι <choice><corr>ὑμῖν</corr><sic>υμειν</sic></choice> 

    <lb n="12"/><hi rend="diaeresis">ἵ</hi>να <subst><add place="inline">ἑκάστης</add><del rend="corrected">εκαστηου</del></subst> οὐσίας ἕνα τινὰ φρον-

    <lb n="13"/>τιστὴν ἀξι<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ό</supplied>χρεων κινδύνῳ ἑκάστης 

    <lb n="14"/>βουλῆς αἱρεθῆναι <subst><add place="inline">ποιήσητε</add><del rend="corrected">ποιησαττε</del></subst>, τὰ δὲ 


    <lb n="15"/>λοιπὰ ὀνόματα παύσηται, δυναμένου 

    <lb n="16"/>τοῦ αἱρουμένου φροντιστοῦ δύο <num value="2"/> 

    <lb n="17"/>ἢ τό γε πλεῖστον τρεῖς <num value="3"/> προσ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">αιρε</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῖ</supplied>ν 

    <lb n="18"/>τοὺς ἐξυπηρετησομένους αὐτῷ 

    <lb n="19"/>πρὸς τὴν φροντίδα. οὕτω<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ς αὐ</supplied>τά τε 

    <lb n="20"/>τὰ μάταια ἀναλώματα π<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">α</supplied>ύσεται 

    <lb n="21"/>καὶ αἱ ταμιακαὶ οὐσίαι τῆς προσηκού-

    <lb n="22"/>σης ἐπιμελείας τεύξονται. δηλα-

    <lb n="23"/>δὴ δὲ τοιούτους αἱρεθῆναι <subst><add place="inline"><choice><corr>ποιήσε-

    <lb n="24"/>τε</corr><sic>ποιησειτε</sic></choice></add><del rend="corrected">ποιησειται</del></subst> <app type="BL"><lem resp="1.313"><choice><corr>τοὺ<supplied cert="high" reason="omitted">ς</supplied></corr><sic>του</sic></choice> τοῖς</lem><rdg>τούτοισ</rdg></app> φρον<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">τι</supplied>σταῖς ὑπηρετη-

    <lb n="25"/>σομένους οἳ καὶ βασάνοις ὑποκείσον-

    <lb n="26"/>ται. <subst><add place="inline">ἔρρωσθε</add><del rend="corrected">ερρωσο</del></subst>. 

    <lb n="27"/><expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="5">ε</num> <orig><g type="s-etous"/></orig> καὶ <num value="4">δ</num> <orig><g type="s-etous"/></orig>, Θὼθ <num value="16">ιϛ</num>. </ab></div><div n="meta.20720" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.20720" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="288" notBefore="288" type="textDate" value="0288-09-13">13. Sept. 288</date></p></div><div n="meta.20720" part="N" subtype="general" type="commentary"><p>Zu Z. 1 vgl. ZPE 155, 2006, S. 254-256.</p></div><div n="meta.20720" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">58</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">20720</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">1</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">58</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;1;58" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.20720" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">231</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.20720" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.20720" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikationen</head><listBibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">P.Lond. III 752 descr.</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">W.Chr. 378</bibl><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">Sel. Pap. II 226</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.20720" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="de"><he